<Paragraph FontWeight="Bold" FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="16">
Serialization Demo
</Paragraph>

<Paragraph>This sample demonstrates how to save and restore a Chart control by converting the control to an XAML string, and then converting the XAML string back to a Chart control.</Paragraph>
