</Paragraph>

<Paragraph FontWeight="Bold" FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="16">
Features
</Paragraph>

<List Margin="25,0,0,0">
<ListItem><Paragraph>Serializing the Chart control into a XAML string that represents the control's state and data.</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>Converting the XAML string back to a Chart control using the XamlReader.</Paragraph></ListItem>
</List>


<Paragraph FontWeight="Bold" FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="16">
Interactive Features</Paragraph>


<List Margin="25,0,0,0">
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>Click <Bold>"Save"</Bold> to serialize the chart. For reference, the serialized string can be seen below the chart.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>Click <Bold>"Load"</Bold> to de-serialize the content back into the chart.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>
</List>

